         <abstract id="aspace_aa9f4e31e41389d340f1054e2fade3ea">The materials consist of photographs documenting the construction of Dickinson Hall and Wheelock Hall at Yale. Included are elevation drawings by James Gamble Rogers and construction views.</abstract>
