      <bioghist id="aspace_fd1c35c0b4997c1e9988da0cc363c041">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Dickinson and Wheelock Halls (York-Library Dormitory) were incorporated into Jonathan Edwards College in 1932.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_035ed3d7c459a5d154697580a4f36f3a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs documenting the construction of Dickinson Hall and Wheelock Hall at Yale. Included are elevation drawings by James Gamble Rogers and construction views.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
